    * no-mirror-refresh-%:			Refresh a single import without updating the        
  mirror, i.e. refresh-go will refresh 'imports/go_import.owl'.               
    * mirror-%:				Refresh a single mirror.                                       
                                                                              
    DOSDP templates                                                           
    * dosdp:			Run the DOSDP patterns pipeline: Run tests, then build OWL        
  files from the tables.                                                      
    * patterns:			Alias of the 'dosdp' command                                   
    * pattern_clean:		Delete all temporary pattern files                        
    * dosdp_validation:		Run all validation checks on DOSDP template files and  
  tables                                                                      
    * pattern_schema_checks:	Alias of the 'dosdp_validation' command           
    * update_patterns:		Pull updated patterns listed in dosdp-                  
  patterns/external.txt                                                       
    * dosdp-matches-%:		Run the DOSDP matches/query pipeline as configured in   
  your cl-odk.yaml file.                                                      
    * dosdp-docs-%:                 Generate the documentation for a given    
  DOSDP pipeline.                                                             
                                                                              
    Editor utilities:                                                         
    * validate_idranges:	Make sure your ID ranges file is formatted correctly  
    * normalize_src:	Load and save your cl-edit file after you to make sure    
