    * explain_unsat:	If you have unsatisfiable classes, this command will      
  create a markdown file (tmp/explain_unsat.md) which will explain all your   
  unsatisfiable classes                                                       
    * validate-all-tsv:	Check all your tsv files for possible problems in      
  syntax. Use ALL_TSV_FILES variable to list files                            
    * validate-tsv:		Check a tsv file for syntactic problems with tsvalid. Use  
